  "Notes": [
    {
      "Text": "Security update for GraphicsMagick",
      "Title": "Topic",
      "Type": "Summary"
    },
    {
      "Text": "This update for GraphicsMagick fixes the following issues:\n\n- CVE-2026-25799: Division-by-Zero in YUV sampling factor validation leads to crash (bsc#1258786).\n- CVE-2026-28690: missing bounds check in the MNG encoder can lead to a stack buffer overflow (bsc#1259456).\n- CVE-2026-30883: missing bounds check when encoding a PNG image can lead to a heap buffer over-write (bsc#1259467).\n",
      "Title": "Details",
      "Type": "General"
    },
    {
